s and other events in april  he was a speaker at the startup america summit in phoenix arizona the silicon desert december meetup and the company also presented a free identity theft summit for local law enforcement officials in arizona davis presented at the  south by southwest online privacy nuclear meltdown or nextgen fuel discussions he was selected to speak at the  global ethics summit and participated in the  inside the reporter’s notebook event for the phoenix business journal davis has contributed to forbes magazine and the huffington post with identity theft protection advice for individuals philanthropyedit davis through lifelock contributes to conquer paralysis now and serves on the board of directors the foundation founded in  works to find a cure for paralysis he is an honorary advisor the national organization for victim assistance as well as an honorary board member for bioaccel he’s also on the board of directors for the boys  girls club of greater phoenix recognitionedit davis won the ernst  young entrepreneur of the year for top emerging company for orange county and desert cities in  he was also awarded the crm magazines service elite award the arizona business leadership associations leadership award and arizona business journals  most admired ceos in  referencesedit  class action alleges deceptive marketing by lifelock  fraudprevention pitchman becomes id theft victim  cnncom  interview with todd davis ceo of lifelock  a b online privacy nuclear meltdown or nextgen fuel sxsw  retrieved march     a b lifelock inc bloomberg retrieved march     a b larry greenemeier january   high five meet todd davis ceo of lifelock information week retrieved march     a b lifelock’s todd davis building an awardwinning identity theft protection company corporate review october   retrieved march     how to proactively prevent identity theft internet scambusters retrieved march     david swartz   value investing challenge finalist pdf value investing challenge retri